{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/TGT_ENG_SteamCalloutBanner_1.png?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Stop Nemesis Prime as an Autobot or Decepticon.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/GIF_1_Transformers_GT_Choose_your_side.gif?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Roll out for an intense fusion of arcade racing and robot combat in TRANSFORMERS: Galactic Trials! Evil NEMESIS PRIME has stolen the Prime Relics that bestow incredible powers on whoever possesses them. Now the AUTOBOTS and DECEPTICONS are in an explosive race to recover these powerful artifacts \u2013 which side will you fight for? <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/TGT_ENG_SteamCalloutBanner_2.png?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Compete in a frenetic fusion of racing and combat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/GIF_2_Transformers_GT_Battle_to_the_finish.gif?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Choose your character from icons like BUMBLEBEE, MEGATRON, and OPTIMUS PRIME, and speed into action on ten battle-race circuits. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/TGT_ENG_SteamCalloutBanner_3.png?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Level up and customize 11 iconic Transformers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/GIF_3_Transformers_GT_Level_Customize.gif?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Pull off sick drifts, charge your way through Boost Pads, and build up your Energon meter as you try to outpace your rivals.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/TGT_ENG_SteamCalloutBanner_4.png?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Drift and boost around 10 action-packed tracks <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/GIF_4_Transformers_GT_Speed_to_the_victory.gif?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Then convert into bot-mode and unleash devastating Energon-fueled skills, including OPTIMUS PRIME\u2019s Energon Axe and BUMBLEBEE\u2019s Plasma Sting, to fight your opponents to the finish line. As you gain experience and recover the powerful Prime Relics, you\u2019ll build your skills and unlock new characters and skins. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/TGT_ENG_SteamCalloutBanner_5.png?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>Battle-race a friend in Versus mode.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/GIF_5_Transformers_GT_Local_Multiplayer.gif?t=1728635642\" /><br><br>This is more than a race and bigger than any battle. It\u2019s the ultimate test of your favorite TRANSFORMERS\u2019 robot abilities, which will decide the future of Cybertron!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CHOOSE YOUR SIDE \u2013</strong> Stop Nemesis Prime as an Autobot or Decepticon <br></li><li><strong>BATTLE TO THE FINISH \u2013</strong> Compete in a frenetic fusion of racing and combat  <br></li><li><strong>LEVEL YOUR CHARACTER \u2013</strong> Level up and customize 11 iconic Transformers <br></li><li><strong>SPEED TO VICTORY \u2013</strong> Drift and boost around 10 action-packed tracks <br></li><li><strong>LOCAL MULTIPLAYER \u2013</strong> Battle-race a friend in Versus mode </li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Autobots, Roll Out!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2324210/3e3beddf33201bb1c3a10da283eb4db1aa3290b1.jpg"},{"name":"Decepticons, Attack!!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap